name: PunkForce
description:
Public Domain, Free Mint  27-01-2022, IPFS

PunkForce is a Cyber-Fantasy themed CryptoPunks derivative PFP collection on the Ethereum blockchain, hosted on IPFS,  minted for free, and published in the Public Domain.

Collection is programmatically generated using various traits created in 24px and the contract is deployed using Factoria.app. The contract is set at 0% royalties.

Please note this collection is in no way affiliated with Larva Labs.
